name: The Trees and The Life #010-Benoa
description:
They are often overlooked even though they plays important role in Benoa bay. A lot of people want to turn them to land and resorts no one ever asking, and take a slice of fortune from it. Isn't without reason they're there.

Taman Hutan Raya Ngurah Rai is mangrove protected area around Benoa Bay Bali. It's home to many fish species, crab, clams, also birds.

The Trees and The Life is a 10-Photo-Based-NFT Collection made by Danar Tri Atmojo. As the first-ever collection made, Danar dedicated these NFT's to mother nature as we move towards the new era of digitalization using Tezos blockchain as #CleanNFTs.
